<div class="zm-item" data-type="Answer">
<h2 class="zm-item-title"><a target="_blank" href="/question/286951027">蟑螂是否真的会爬进人耳朵里产卵？</a></h2>
<div class="zm-item-fav">
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-answer "
itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Answer"
data-aid="112484640"
data-atoken="453288624"
data-collapsed="0"
data-created="1532660483"
data-deleted="0"
data-isowner="0"
data-helpful="True"
data-copyable="0"
data-zop
>
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/286951027/answer/453288624">
<meta itemprop="answer-id" content="112484640">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="453288624">
<a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-112484640"></a>

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>14K</a>
</div>

