<div class="zm-item" data-type="Answer">
<h2 class="zm-item-title"><a target="_blank" href="/question/270883846">哪本书是你只要有机会就会强烈推荐的？为什么？</a></h2>
<div class="zm-item-fav">
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-answer "
itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Answer"
data-aid="102712683"
data-atoken="399535738"
data-collapsed="0"
