<div class="zm-item" data-type="Answer">
<h2 class="zm-item-title"><a target="_blank" href="/question/285361548">如何看待「国家药监局飞检长春长生发现违法违规行为」，「涉事狂犬病疫苗未流向市场」？</a></h2>
<div class="zm-item-fav">
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-answer "
